<subSubSection id="C3326E8AFFFAC10C7FD7FA45FCAAF009" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B973D01FFFAC10C7FD7FA45FCAAF009" blockId="10.[136,1452,1526,1625]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7FD7FA45FDD8F041" authority="Bosch &amp; Sande Lac." authorityName="Bosch &amp; Sande Lac." box="[136,577,1526,1553]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Hypnum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="similans">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7FD7FA45FED4F040" box="[136,333,1526,1552]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Hypnum similans</emphasis>
Bosch &amp; Sande Lac.
</taxonomicName>
was described as an Indonesian species distributed in Java (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFFAC10C7BADFA44FA06F040" author="Fleischer, M." box="[1266,1439,1526,1552]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="1105 - 1729" refId="ref8364" refString="Fleischer, M. (1923) Musci Buitenzorg 4. Brill, Leiden, i - xxxi + pp. 1105 - 1729." type="book chapter" year="1923">Fleischer 1923</bibRefCitation>
). The species has been listed in moss flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFFAC10C7D24F9A8FD27F064" box="[635,702,1562,1588]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">China</collectingCountry>
based on a specimen from 
<collectingRegion id="49ECF3E3FFFAC10C7CABF9A8FB37F064" box="[1012,1198,1562,1588]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Hainan province</collectingRegion>
[
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7BE0F9A9FA32F064" box="[1215,1451,1562,1589]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">P.-C. Chen et al. 574</emphasis>
(PE)]. Our examination reveals it to be 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7D1DF98CFCB5F008" authorityName="W. R. Buck" authorityYear="1987" baseAuthorityName="Cardot" box="[578,812,1598,1624]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Phyllodon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="lingulatus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7D1DF98CFCB5F008" box="[578,812,1598,1624]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Phyllodon lingulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
